    <bug_when>2012-06-20 15:16:53 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>The EPUB Ant task has been designed to assemble an EPUB using existing items in form of images and XHTML files. However it is also desirable to be able to assemble an EPUB directly from other sources, such as Wiki markup. 

Such an Ant task would share many properties with the existing task and because of this the various types in the the EPUB should be exposed for re-use.</thetext>
